=================== MSDN Flash ====================

All the developer news from Microsoft in one e-mail. For more information, tools, and community resources, visit MSDN Online at http://msdn.microsoft.com/

==================================================

Last week you may have received a Special MSDN Flash which identified you as a past Developer Days attendee, and indicated you are not currently subscribed to our regular MSDN Flash newsletter. Although the salutation identified recipients as being Dev Day 2000 event attendees the message was intended for all recipients. Receiving this email indicates that you are subscribed to the MSDN Flash email newsletter. We hope you will be able to attend the Dev Days 2001 event on November 6 or 8. To cancel your subscription to this newsletter, or stop all newsletters from microsoft.com, read the directions at the bottom of this message.

