* Microsoft .NET Developer Training Available near you
During this two-day seminar, talented instructors will demonstrate step-by-step the building of an entirely new intranet application utilizing existing XML Web services on the Internet. Register today at a location near you for only U.S.$499 with RSVP code 40271. (U.S. Only)
